7. Product Strategy

Clinora will initially launch as a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform.

Every clinic will receive its own secure environment while sharing a common cloud infrastructure.

Each clinic will have:

Independent users
Independent doctors
Independent patients
Independent appointments
Independent medical records
Independent reports
Independent billing
Independent analytics

This multi-tenant architecture enables scalability while maintaining complete data isolation between clinics.

